{"tid":13904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【代理打架】逾十名代理浪澄灣外毆鬥","createTime":"2016-11-30T09:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T11:20:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"542e0c9acb2bbc4999f3e15559e4dc365195c031","tid":13904,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/172842_126590d62aaed13516b09b7ba15a119f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F172842_126590d62aaed13516b09b7ba15a119f.jpg&h=a97ff27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府出招後，新盤市場淡靜，樓齡達12年的恒隆地產（101）大角嘴浪澄灣將於本周六發售，成為辣招後首個開售新盤。或許因市道淡靜，餓盤多時的地產代理蜂擁而出搵客，導致又再發生疑搶客大打出手。<br />\n<br />\n根據網上瘋傳一段影片，有逾10名擬似地產代理在街上追逐群毆，事發地點為浪澄灣對開的海輝道，據知涉及兩間地產代理行。<br />\n<br />\n短片所見，有最少4人圍毆一名倒地的擬似代理。亦有兩名代理互相揮拳，並倒地扭作一團，又箍頸又夾腳。另有最少兩人手上持有由紙捲成的棍狀物體，向其他人作出攻擊，場面混亂，未知打架起因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55986074&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55986074%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161130&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=e0244eaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55986074%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161130&h=04218352\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55986074&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161130</a>"},{"pid":"b806610f99a8f839894f1c553c7e2e969899cd16","tid":13904,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"